rows.label: tlk70000042_01_msg0001
rows.name:
What do you think? Don't all these fish
look happy and healthy? Feisty critters!
I tell you, they've got it good.

rows.label: tlk70000042_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm even selling fish to the palace now.
Considering who my customer is, I really
want to provide the best I can.

rows.label: tlk70000042_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Hey, what do you mean, my
fish don't look good enough
to sell to the palace?

rows.label: tlk70000042_01_msg0004
rows.name:
See how many big, glossy fish are
swimming around in the moat? Every one
of them started out in these pails!
